thread.title_full: Autoclick Rent a Car evaluado por Customer William hurliw

author: Customer William hurliw
title: Customer William hurliw
text: I have used this company several times, and can say each time I have received excellent service from all the staff I have encountered. However the printer is old and in reality outdated. The amount of time it takes to print out each hirer's paperwork can lead to delays. PLEASE PLEASE INVESTMENT IN A MODERN LASER PRINTER !!! OTHERWISE EXCELLENT.
